ottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  will get sued for fraud</a>=
=C2=A0<em>because you published a code of ethics.</em>=C2=A0=E2=80=9CYou sa=
id you have a code of ethics, which implied that your executives were ethic=
al, but you neglected to mention that one of them wasn=E2=80=99t.=E2=80=9D<=
/p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This concept is really <a href=3D"https://link=
